create a ssh key
-------------------------------------------------
ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C "rapps9999@gmail.com"
--- never give -C, just generate a local ssh key and add it. by that you can recognise by the key from where you have committed the code

cat /Users/pereirar/.ssh/id_rsa.pub

upload it to github

add ssh key ( can skip - you have to provide the passwork everytime )
----------------------------------
eval `/volume/buildtools/bin/ssh-agent.sh --and-link`
ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa
